jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Py","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":38537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/24\/allah-faces-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26260,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah faces him in prayer unless he looks elsewhere","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty continues to face towards the servant while he is in prayer as long as he does not avert his eyes. If he looks elsewhere, Allah will turn elsewhere.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 909 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":26260,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s supplication in Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he finished his Witr prayer with invocations of peace, he would say, \u201cGlory to the King, the Holy.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1430 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Rig