/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17191,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/prophet-cries-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":26260,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet weeps during his prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mutarrif reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was praying. His chest made a sound like a boiling water pot from his crying. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 904 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0637\u064e\u0631\u0651\u0650\u0641\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/mindful-friday-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26260,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jumu\u2019ah: Have presence at sermon, be near to Imam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe present at the sermon and come close to the Imam. Verily, a man continues to distance himself until he is delayed from Paradise, even though he will eventually enter it.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom 